          <gco:CharacterString>This is a map service that is geared towards the dissemination of large datasets, particularly LiDAR elevation data collects. Data can be downloaded by selections of tiles using individual, box graphic, polygon graphic, or by GIS polygon features. Currently contains LiDAR collects for the Red River Valley (2009), Maple River (2003), Sheyenne River (2002), and Bismarck/Mandan (2009).</gco:CharacterString>         </gmd:abstract>
